19 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 3-101, as
20 amended by Section 1, Chapter 182, O.S.L. 2023 (70 O.S. Supp. 2024,
21 Section 3-101), is amended to read as follows:
22 Section 3-101. A. The State Board of Education shall consist
23 of seven (7) eleven (11) members. The State Superintendent of
24
